---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Boxing Timer Champ">
  <main class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-golden mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">About Boxing Timer Champ</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-elegant-text-secondary mb-8">
          Boxing Timer Champ is designed for serious boxing training, offering precision, reliability, and a clean user experience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-golden mb-4">Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
            The mission of Boxing Timer Champ is to build the most user-friendly boxing timer on the market. The app empowers athletes and coaches to take complete control of their training, offering an intuitive experience that makes every workout efficient and enjoyable.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-golden mb-4">Why Choose Boxing Timer Champ?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-8 flex">There are many boxing timer apps. Here's why Boxing Timer Champ is the top contender.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center"><i class="fas fa-clock text-green-500 mr-3 text-2xl"></i>Precision First</h3>
              <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
                Built with input from fighters, Boxing Timer Champ ensures every second counts for effective training.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-green-500 mr-3 text-2xl"></i>Battle Tested</h3>
              <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
                Trusted by professional fighters and coaches worldwide, this timer stands up to the toughest training sessions.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center"><i class="fas fa-sync-alt text-green-500 mr-3 text-2xl"></i>Always Evolving</h3>
              <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
                Boxing Timer Champ evolves with feedback from the boxing community, ensuring it meets the needs of athletes everywhere.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center"><i class="fas fa-users text-green-500 mr-3 text-2xl"></i>Community Focused</h3>
              <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
                The app is built to support the boxing community, providing tools that help fighters reach their goals.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-golden mb-4 drop-shadow-md">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
            For questions or feedback, please send a message via the <a href="/contact" class="text-green-500 underline hover:text-golden">contact page</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
